<H4>Environment Reservation System</H4>
<HR>
<B> <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-cloud" aria-hidden="true"></span> PURPOSE OF THIS APPLICATION:</B>
<BR><P>This application allows users to checkout development environments that are used for testing new features.
This enables the engineering staff from breaking environments while being tested on real hardware.
<BR>
<BR>
<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-console" aria-hidden="true"></span> The flow of this application is as following:
<BR>
<BR>
<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></span> 1.) User select environment that is not currently in use.
<BR>
<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></span> 2.) Users Checkout environment and notification is sent to Hipchat.
<BR>
<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></span> 3.) Dashboard show current user of each environment and time that the user has checked out the environment.
<BR>
<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></span> 4.) Users releases environment back to pool and status of release is sent to hipchat. </P>
